{"tid":1252414,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【輿論戰第一回合】防止父母被分化！","createTime":"2019-06-23T04:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T11:31:53.000Z","uid":238051,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b64cb60aea2e54e861220b153769481ae334f6","tid":1252414,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"呢段片喺一日間已在FB, TG及Whatsapp廣傳：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1261483650723574&amp;id=368513580020590&amp;fs=0&amp;focus_composer=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1261483650723574%26id%3D368513580020590%26fs%3D0%26focus_composer%3D0&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=d50b275d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1261483650723574&amp;id=368513580020590&amp;fs=0&amp;focus_composer=0</a><br />\n<br />\n而暫時搵到最原始嘅發布<br />\n就喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>連登</strong></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［致年青人：你哋無上街嘅父母根本無愛過你］</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246598</a><br />\n唔想幫佢做宣傳，所以內容煩請巴絲入去睇<br />\n<br />\n上面個post嘅樓主留咗兩次言就失去蹤跡<br />\n留低嘅youtube片亦已刪除<br />\n但片段已於各大小藍絲群組廣泛散播<br />\n甚至已有抗爭人士嘅父母信以為真<br />\n覺得段片係我地嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請各位幫忙澄清<br />\n呢段片<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>絕非</strong></span>眾抗爭者立場！<br />\n<br />\n相信呢類反宣傳行動會陸續有來<br />\n希望眾巴絲動員最大力量打呢場輿論戰！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>拒絕</strong></span>被港共建制惡意黑化抗命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15427d98fadabebd071009f5e3559cfc89